snippet.title: Amber Heard apologist: simping ain't easy
snippet.description: This is a video about things I've seen and people starting conversations. And 100% not taking the evidence as it is. How ever instead trying to use stuff from 30 years ago to make some guilty and I got into a conversation with a few people. So here are my thoughts on this situation and these apologist who clearly ignore evidence and some experiences I've had.
